OL,3,CJersey savers at 'disadvantage' over
OL,4,CUK if their bank goes bust
OL,6,FThe maximum level of compensation in
OL,7,FJersey has not changed since its
OL,8,Fintroduction in 2009, despite
OL,9,Finflation increasing by more than 65%
OL,10,Fsince then.
OL,12,FThe Economic and International Affairs
OL,13,FScrutiny Panel has decided to begin a
OL,14,Freview after being "disappointed" that
OL,15,Fa limit increase was not among the
OL,16,Fproposed changes to Jersey's financial
OL,17,Flaw.
OL,19,FThe review will "consider whether the
OL,20,Flimit should be increased and the
OL,21,Fpotential impacts of altering".
