OL,3,CJersey savers at 'disadvantage' over
OL,4,CUK if their bank goes bust
OL,6,FChair of the Panel, Deputy Montfort
OL,7,FTadier, says: "We feel this leaves
OL,8,Fsavers in Jersey at a disadvantage
OL,9,Fover their counterparts in other
OL,10,Fjurisdictions and feel that further
OL,11,Fconsultation on the limit would have
OL,12,Fbeen useful in this matter.
OL,14,F"An argument has been presented to
OL,15,Frationalise the current compensation
OL,16,Flimit in line with those set in
OL,17,FGuernsey and the Isle of Man, and that
OL,18,Fit is appropriate and proportionate
OL,19,Ffor the size of the island.
