OL,3,CJersey savers at 'disadvantage' over
OL,4,CUK if their bank goes bust
OL,6,F"However, the Panel is aware that
OL,7,Fother small jurisdictions such as
OL,8,FGibraltar allow for compensation
OL,9,Flimits of E100,000 which, once
OL,10,Fconverted, would put it more on par
OL,11,Fwith the UK."
OL,13,FThe Panel is asking for people with
OL,14,Fsavings to get in touch to share their
OL,15,Fviews - it will then present its
OL,16,Frecommendations to the States Assembly
OL,17,Fin September.
